minicluster (1.0.16-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Go API server replaces .NET backend — single static binary, no runtime required
  * Container lifecycle management (Docker/Podman)
  * Multi-component package registry (v2 manifest schema)
  * Container metrics integration
  * CLI inspection, package init/build/validate/push commands

